---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const title = "Male African Grey Parrots for Sale | DNA-Sexed — C.A.Gs, Midland TX | Hand-Raised Males";
const description = "Buy DNA-sexed male African grey parrots. Hand-raised, vet-checked, CITES-documented. Male greys known for exceptional talking ability. Ships nationwide from Texas.";
const canonical = "https://congoafricangreys.com/male-african-gray-for-sale/";

const schemaJson = JSON.stringify({
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Product",
  "name": "Male African Grey Parrot for Sale",
  "description": "Hand-raised, DNA-sexed male African Grey parrots. CITES-documented, vet-certified, USDA-licensed breeder in Midland, TX.",
  "url": canonical,
  "brand": { "@type": "Brand", "name": "Congo African Greys (C.A.Gs)" },
  "offers": {
    "@type": "AggregateOffer",
    "lowPrice": "1600",
    "highPrice": "3500",
    "priceCurrency": "USD",
    "availability": "https://schema.org/InStock"
  }
});
---

<BaseLayout {title} {description} {canonical} {schemaJson}>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-logo-dark text-cream py-16 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="text-gold font-sora text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">DNA-Sexed Males · Hand-Raised · Ships Nationwide</p>
      <h1 class="font-lora font-bold text-4xl sm:text-5xl mb-4">Male African Gray Parrots for Sale</h1>
      <p class="text-cream/80 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8">Known for exceptional talking ability and bold personalities — our male African grey parrots are hand-raised, DNA-certified, and CITES-documented. From $1,600.</p>
      <a href="/contact-us/" class="inline-block bg-clay text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-full hover:bg-clay-dk transition-colors">
        Inquire About Male Greys →
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Trust bar -->
  <div class="bg-green/10 border-y border-green/20 py-3 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6 text-sm text-green font-sora font-semibold">
      <span>✔ DNA Sexing Certificate Included</span>
      <span>✔ CITES Captive-Bred Documentation</span>
      <span>✔ USDA AWA Licensed Breeder</span>
      <span>✔ Health Guarantee</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">

    <!-- Intro -->
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-10">
      <p>Welcome to Congo African Greys (C.A.Gs) — your trusted source for hand-raised male African grey parrots from Midland, Texas. Male African grey parrots are renowned for their exceptional talking ability, bold personalities, and deep bonding with their owners. Every male grey we offer is:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>DNA-sexed with a certified laboratory report</li>
        <li>Fully weaned and socialized by our breeders</li>
        <li>Vet-checked with complete health records</li>
        <li>CITES Appendix II captive-bred documentation included</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We provide nationwide shipping via Delta or United Airlines cargo for just $185. Your bird arrives in an IATA-compliant carrier, hand-delivered by our experienced bird handlers.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Why Male Greys -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="font-lora font-bold text-2xl text-green mb-6">Why Choose a Male African Grey Parrot?</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-green/5 border border-green/20 rounded-xl p-5">
          <h3 class="font-lora font-semibold text-green mb-3">🗣 Superior Talking Ability</h3>
          <p class="text-sm">Male African grey parrots are often more talkative and develop a wider vocabulary faster than females. They mimic voices, household sounds, and full phrases with remarkable accuracy.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-green/5 border border-green/20 rounded-xl p-5">
          <h3 class="font-lora font-semibold text-green mb-3">🤝 Deep Human Bonding</h3>
          <p class="text-sm">Males bond strongly with their primary caregiver. With consistent interaction and training, a male grey becomes a lifelong companion who anticipates your routines and moods.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-green/5 border border-green/20 rounded-xl p-5">
          <h3 class="font-lora font-semibold text-green mb-3">🎭 Bold, Playful Personality</h3>
          <p class="text-sm">Male greys tend to be more energetic and curious. They're explorers by nature — always investigating new toys, sounds, and people. Great for active households.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-green/5 border border-green/20 rounded-xl p-5">
          <h3 class="font-lora font-semibold text-green mb-3">📊 Larger Build</h3>
          <p class="text-sm">Males are generally slightly larger and bulkier than females — a subtle physical distinction confirmed through DNA testing, not just visual inspection.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-4">Compare male and female African greys in detail: <a href="/male-vs-female-african-grey-parrots-for-sale/" class="text-green hover:text-clay">8 Key Differences Between Male vs Female African Grey Parrots</a>.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- What's Included -->
    <section class="mb-12 bg-cream border border-gold/30 rounded-2xl p-6">
      <h2 class="font-lora font-bold text-xl text-green mb-4">What's Included With Every Male African Grey</h2>
      <ul class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-sm">
        <li class="flex gap-2">✔ <span>DNA sexing laboratory certificate confirming male</span></li>
        <li class="flex gap-2">✔ <span>Complete avian vet health check report</span></li>
        <li class="flex gap-2">✔ <span>CITES captive-bred documentation</span></li>
        <li class="flex gap-2">✔ <span>USDA AWA licensed breeder paperwork</span></li>
        <li class="flex gap-2">✔ <span>Health guarantee (see our <a href="/african-greys-for-sale-with-health-guarantee/" class="text-green hover:text-clay">health guarantee page</a>)</span></li>
        <li class="flex gap-2">✔ <span>Nationwide IATA-compliant air shipping ($185)</span></li>
        <li class="flex gap-2">✔ <span>Starter diet recommendations from our breeders</span></li>
        <li class="flex gap-2">✔ <span>Post-purchase breeder support</span></li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- Pricing -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="font-lora font-bold text-2xl text-green mb-4">Male African Grey Parrot Pricing</h2>
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p>Male Congo African Grey parrots are priced between <strong>$1,600 and $3,500</strong> depending on age, training level, and current availability. Price includes DNA sexing certificate, vet records, and CITES documentation.</p>
        <p>For full pricing context across all variants, see our <a href="/african-grey-parrot-for-sale/">African Grey Parrots for Sale</a> page, or <a href="/contact-us/">contact us directly</a> for the current availability list.</p>
        <p>🐦 Prefer to compare? <a href="/congo-african-grey-for-sale/">Congo African Grey for Sale</a> · <a href="/african-grey-breeding-pair-for-sale/">Breeding Pairs</a> · <a href="/african-grey-parrot-bird-eggs-for-sale-usa/">Fertile Eggs</a></p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="bg-logo-dark text-cream rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-lora font-bold text-2xl mb-3">Ready to Meet Your Male African Grey?</h2>
      <p class="text-cream/80 mb-6">Contact C.A.Gs to get the current list of available male African grey parrots. All birds are DNA-sexed, vet-certified, and CITES-documented.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 justify-center">
        <a href="/contact-us/" class="bg-clay text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-full hover:bg-clay-dk transition-colors">Inquire Now →</a>
        <a href="/male-vs-female-african-grey-parrots-for-sale/" class="border border-cream/40 text-cream font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-full hover:border-gold hover:text-gold transition-colors">Male vs Female Guide</a>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xs text-cream/50 mt-4">2508 Briaroaks Ct · Midland, Texas 79707 · (956) 564-6067</p>
    </section>

  </article>

</BaseLayout>
